ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, it's good to know the topics covered in this class.
The course is similar to Econometrics II, but is more theoretical and it goes more into depth on a lot of results. I would highly recommend the course.
He is a really good instructor.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: too theoretical -- yuichi started the class with metrics that is applicable and interesting to many fields, but then we went deeper into theory than expected, which i had not expected, and so it was not that helpful.
The course provided me with additional tools to tackle problems in econometrics, and made me aware of some of the problems that may arise.
I don't choose to become an econometrician. If otherwise this course would be very helpfull-.
